00:31:17.000 --> 00:31:19.400 align:middle line:84%
>> What are the Lifeline
manifestation steps?

00:31:19.400 --> 00:31:20.500 align:middle line:90%
I want to understand this.

00:31:20.500 --> 00:31:21.650 align:middle line:90%
>> That's cool.

00:31:21.650 --> 00:31:27.110 align:middle line:84%
So the manifestation steps
are about getting present.

00:31:27.110 --> 00:31:29.350 align:middle line:84%
And that's through a process
called the connection.

00:31:29.350 --> 00:31:31.630 align:middle line:84%
It establishes
present-time consciousness.

00:31:31.630 --> 00:31:35.320 align:middle line:84%
Another way to look at that is
before I play an instrument,

00:31:35.320 --> 00:31:36.880 align:middle line:90%
I've gotta tune it.

00:31:36.880 --> 00:31:40.300 align:middle line:84%
So this is an incredible
instrument, our mind, our body,

00:31:40.300 --> 00:31:43.030 align:middle line:84%
our spirit, our
connection to the Earth,

00:31:43.030 --> 00:31:45.410 align:middle line:90%
our connection to the universe.

00:31:45.410 --> 00:31:47.830 align:middle line:84%
So there's a
step-by-step process

00:31:47.830 --> 00:31:52.960 align:middle line:84%
in the manifestation system
where we tune our instrument.

00:31:52.960 --> 00:31:56.350 align:middle line:84%
The second aspect of
the manifestation system

00:31:56.350 --> 00:31:58.040 align:middle line:90%
is about setting intention.

00:31:58.040 --> 00:31:59.960 align:middle line:84%
And there's four
particular parts.

00:31:59.960 --> 00:32:02.230 align:middle line:84%
It's about observing
the portals.

00:32:02.230 --> 00:32:04.180 align:middle line:84%
Where's your body
speaking to you?

00:32:04.180 --> 00:32:10.300 align:middle line:84%
What are the diseases that are
going on physically, mentally?

00:32:10.300 --> 00:32:12.250 align:middle line:90%
Where are you stressed in life?

00:32:12.250 --> 00:32:13.450 align:middle line:90%
Financially?

00:32:13.450 --> 00:32:15.040 align:middle line:90%
Relationship-wise?

00:32:15.040 --> 00:32:16.450 align:middle line:90%
Family?

00:32:16.450 --> 00:32:18.190 align:middle line:90%
We observe those first.

00:32:18.190 --> 00:32:22.070 align:middle line:84%
We take inventory rather than
getting caught in the story,

00:32:22.070 --> 00:32:22.870 align:middle line:90%
right?

00:32:22.870 --> 00:32:23.870 align:middle line:90%
And we acknowledge.

00:32:23.870 --> 00:32:26.710 align:middle line:84%
Because that's the
subconscious mind.

00:32:26.710 --> 00:32:29.350 align:middle line:84%
Those symptoms and
stressors are the tip

00:32:29.350 --> 00:32:31.870 align:middle line:84%
of the iceberg what's
below the surface.

00:32:31.870 --> 00:32:32.840 align:middle line:90%
So we acknowledge it.

00:32:32.840 --> 00:32:36.820 align:middle line:84%
Then we ask what's
called a truth question.

00:32:36.820 --> 00:32:40.295 align:middle line:84%
And that enables us to shift
judgment into discernment.

00:32:40.295 --> 00:32:42.670 align:middle line:84%
Because you know, after we
observe symptoms and stressors

00:32:42.670 --> 00:32:44.660 align:middle line:84%
in our body, we start
judging ourselves.

00:32:44.660 --> 00:32:45.460 align:middle line:90%
I'm a failure.

00:32:45.460 --> 00:32:46.440 align:middle line:90%
I'm sick.

00:32:46.440 --> 00:32:47.240 align:middle line:90%
I'm weak.

00:32:47.240 --> 00:32:48.570 align:middle line:90%
I'm not good enough.

00:32:48.570 --> 00:32:51.220 align:middle line:84%
But judgment won't do
anything to move us forward.

00:32:51.220 --> 00:32:53.540 align:middle line:84%
So we ask a question, and
it's a real simple question,

00:32:53.540 --> 00:32:55.360 align:middle line:84%
but it's a
game-changing question.

00:32:55.360 --> 00:32:57.730 align:middle line:84%
Hey, if you could choose
to create your life--

00:32:57.730 --> 00:32:58.900 align:middle line:90%
a day or moment--

00:32:58.900 --> 00:33:02.920 align:middle line:84%
this disease of
autoimmune disease,

00:33:02.920 --> 00:33:05.440 align:middle line:84%
this pain in your back,
this digestive challenge,

00:33:05.440 --> 00:33:09.280 align:middle line:84%
that anxiety, that
fear, that anger,

00:33:09.280 --> 00:33:11.530 align:middle line:84%
would you choose to create
your life with this?

00:33:11.530 --> 00:33:14.500 align:middle line:84%
And everyone that's
asked this question

00:33:14.500 --> 00:33:15.560 align:middle line:90%
answers it the same way.

00:33:15.560 --> 00:33:17.310 align:middle line:84%
That's why it's called
the truth question.

00:33:17.310 --> 00:33:18.710 align:middle line:90%
The answer is, hell no.

00:33:18.710 --> 00:33:19.510 align:middle line:90%
Hell no.

00:33:19.510 --> 00:33:20.890 align:middle line:90%
No one chooses cancer.

00:33:20.890 --> 00:33:24.040 align:middle line:84%
Not one person has ever
chosen anaphylactic allergies.

00:33:24.040 --> 00:33:26.230 align:middle line:90%
No one chooses to be an addict.

00:33:26.230 --> 00:33:28.130 align:middle line:90%
This is the subconscious mind.

00:33:28.130 --> 00:33:30.240 align:middle line:84%
So once we ask that
question, now we're

00:33:30.240 --> 00:33:32.850 align:middle line:84%
in a discerning place rather
than judgmental place.

00:33:32.850 --> 00:33:35.940 align:middle line:84%
And now we can lead
the subconscious mind.

00:33:35.940 --> 00:33:39.510 align:middle line:84%
And now we follow particular,
what I call two golden rules

00:33:39.510 --> 00:33:41.490 align:middle line:90%
for setting intention.

00:33:41.490 --> 00:33:44.700 align:middle line:84%
We use our imagination
to bring out

00:33:44.700 --> 00:33:48.120 align:middle line:84%
a feeling tone of what it
feels like to imagine ourselves

00:33:48.120 --> 00:33:50.250 align:middle line:90%
already as our best self.

00:33:50.250 --> 00:33:51.360 align:middle line:90%
And that feeling?

00:33:51.360 --> 00:33:53.390 align:middle line:90%
That's the mind medicine.

00:33:53.390 --> 00:33:56.300 align:middle line:84%
When we're feeling
our future self--

00:33:56.300 --> 00:33:59.360 align:middle line:84%
healthy, strong,
confident, brave, right?

00:33:59.360 --> 00:34:01.070 align:middle line:84%
Living the life
we love to live--

00:34:01.070 --> 00:34:06.860 align:middle line:84%
that feeling that we get inside,
light, powerful, grounded,

00:34:06.860 --> 00:34:07.970 align:middle line:90%
that's actual medicine.

00:34:07.970 --> 00:34:11.090 align:middle line:84%
Those are chemical reactions
going on inside of the body

00:34:11.090 --> 00:34:15.170 align:middle line:84%
because we use our mind
properly as a tool.

00:34:15.170 --> 00:34:17.201 align:middle line:84%
So these are the
manifestation steps.

00:34:17.201 --> 00:34:19.409 align:middle line:84%
>> You mentioned something
called the truth question.

00:34:19.409 --> 00:34:21.020 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:34:21.020 --> 00:34:23.659 align:middle line:84%
>> Maybe just explain a little
bit more of that specifically.

00:34:23.659 --> 00:34:25.909 align:middle line:84%
Why is that important
in this technique?

00:34:25.909 --> 00:34:28.159 align:middle line:84%
>> And it's so important
not just in this technique,

00:34:28.159 --> 00:34:29.389 align:middle line:90%
in life.

00:34:29.389 --> 00:34:34.469 align:middle line:84%
When we ask ourself, would
I choose to feel this way?

00:34:34.469 --> 00:34:36.370 align:middle line:84%
Would I choose to
think this way?

00:34:36.370 --> 00:34:39.290 align:middle line:84%
Would I choose what
I'm experiencing

00:34:39.290 --> 00:34:42.409 align:middle line:84%
in my body, in my
marriage, in my business?

00:34:42.409 --> 00:34:45.860 align:middle line:84%
And when it's painful, when
it's scary, when it's stressful,

00:34:45.860 --> 00:34:47.989 align:middle line:90%
the answer's no.

00:34:47.989 --> 00:34:49.639 align:middle line:90%
I wouldn't choose it.

00:34:49.639 --> 00:34:52.250 align:middle line:84%
I might say, you know, something
good will come from it.

00:34:52.250 --> 00:34:53.790 align:middle line:90%
But that's not the question.

00:34:53.790 --> 00:34:55.989 align:middle line:84%
The question is,
would you choose it?

00:34:55.989 --> 00:34:59.360 align:middle line:84%
And this is really important
because when we're aware--

00:34:59.360 --> 00:35:01.790 align:middle line:84%
and we're very aware when
we're observing the symptoms

00:35:01.790 --> 00:35:03.230 align:middle line:90%
and stressors of our life--

00:35:03.230 --> 00:35:04.220 align:middle line:90%
we are conscious.

00:35:04.220 --> 00:35:05.450 align:middle line:90%
And guess what?

00:35:05.450 --> 00:35:07.400 align:middle line:84%
When we're conscious,
we, as human beings,

00:35:07.400 --> 00:35:09.740 align:middle line:84%
have something that's
extremely powerful.

00:35:09.740 --> 00:35:11.450 align:middle line:84%
And that is, when
we're conscious,

00:35:11.450 --> 00:35:13.978 align:middle line:90%
we have the power to choose.

00:35:13.978 --> 00:35:16.020 align:middle line:84%
So when we're aware of
something that, of course,

00:35:16.020 --> 00:35:17.450 align:middle line:90%
we would never choose--

00:35:17.450 --> 00:35:19.910 align:middle line:90%
hell no, I'd never choose this--

00:35:19.910 --> 00:35:22.970 align:middle line:84%
what we're aware of is
not the active choosing

00:35:22.970 --> 00:35:26.090 align:middle line:84%
part of ourself,
we've made contact

00:35:26.090 --> 00:35:30.170 align:middle line:84%
with the reactive
program part of ourself.

00:35:30.170 --> 00:35:34.970 align:middle line:84%
We've bridged the gap to
the subconscious mind.

00:35:34.970 --> 00:35:36.890 align:middle line:90%
And now we've made contact.

00:35:36.890 --> 00:35:39.140 align:middle line:90%
And now we can begin--

00:35:39.140 --> 00:35:41.510 align:middle line:84%
as a result of answering
this truth question,

00:35:41.510 --> 00:35:46.130 align:middle line:84%
we can begin to lead and
guide and nurture and support

00:35:46.130 --> 00:35:47.240 align:middle line:90%
this part of ourself.

00:35:47.240 --> 00:35:49.850 align:middle line:84%
Rather than being driven
by our subconscious mind,

00:35:49.850 --> 00:35:55.290 align:middle line:84%
we can influence it to be its
fullest and greatest potential.

