a choice in how you respond.

00:39:35.810 --> 00:39:39.480 align:middle line:84%
And the two golden
rules are how to set

00:39:39.480 --> 00:39:43.800 align:middle line:84%
intention to manifest
sustainable change,

00:39:43.800 --> 00:39:45.880 align:middle line:84%
rather than just
short-term change.

00:39:45.880 --> 00:39:48.450 align:middle line:84%
And the first
golden rule is based

00:39:48.450 --> 00:39:50.880 align:middle line:90%
upon what we focus on grows.

00:39:50.880 --> 00:39:53.740 align:middle line:84%
So we always focus
on where we're going.

00:39:53.740 --> 00:39:58.630 align:middle line:84%
What fear does to us is fear
says, just make this go away.

00:39:58.630 --> 00:40:00.450 align:middle line:84%
Make the symptom,
make the disease,

00:40:00.450 --> 00:40:02.190 align:middle line:90%
make the person just go away.

00:40:02.190 --> 00:40:03.270 align:middle line:90%
Then I can be happy.

00:40:03.270 --> 00:40:04.230 align:middle line:90%
Just avoid this.

00:40:04.230 --> 00:40:05.250 align:middle line:90%
Pretend it's not there.

00:40:05.250 --> 00:40:06.300 align:middle line:90%
That's what fear does.

00:40:06.300 --> 00:40:09.570 align:middle line:84%
And fear will never
create sustainable change.

00:40:09.570 --> 00:40:11.820 align:middle line:90%
Love says, this sucks.

00:40:11.820 --> 00:40:15.180 align:middle line:84%
However, I'm the
common denominator.

00:40:15.180 --> 00:40:18.690 align:middle line:84%
Of everything and everyone in
my life, and if I desire change,

00:40:18.690 --> 00:40:22.500 align:middle line:84%
I've got to take responsibility
for exactly where I am.

00:40:22.500 --> 00:40:24.720 align:middle line:84%
And that responsibility
is the ability

00:40:24.720 --> 00:40:28.550 align:middle line:84%
to respond in the
face of reaction.

00:40:28.550 --> 00:40:30.330 align:middle line:84%
And so the first
golden rule is, instead

00:40:30.330 --> 00:40:32.455 align:middle line:84%
of looking in the rear view
mirror or the side view

00:40:32.455 --> 00:40:34.530 align:middle line:84%
